# MuseDAM Final Validation & Quality Gate (Last Step)

## Trigger

- Always run as the VERY LAST step before outputting any TSX code, after the full MuseDAM workflow and prompt contract have been applied.

## Mandatory Checklist (AI must verify and report)

1. Colors: use simplified Tailwind classes (`text-primary-6`, `bg-success-1`, etc.)? (no `text-[var(--xxx)]`, no hard hex)
2. Spacing: only gap-*/p-* ? (no margin between siblings)
3. Radius: Button/Input=6px, Card=8px, Modal=12px?
4. Icons:
    - 所有 `<Icon name>` 值与 Figma 原始 data-name 完全一致？
    - `public/icons/` 中对应 SVG 文件存在？
    - 无 `currentColor` 以外的硬编码颜色？
    - 无 `lucide-react` 用于已有 Figma 图标的情况？

5. Components: reused existing or correctly placed in domain folder? (07 mapper used)
6. Typography: exact designer scale (22/32 H5, 14/22 body, etc.)?
7. Dark mode: .dark class compatible + ThemeProvider used?
8. Annotations: data-component="..." present for every major element?
9. Responsive: w-full + max-w-7xl + no fixed 1440px?
10. shadcn: all primitives from ui/ and styled with MuseDAM?
11. Fidelity: typography quartet and non-standard spacing/effects either mapped or listed in `Unmapped tokens`?
12. Visual validation:
    - Figma screenshot captured?
    - Local page screenshot captured with `playwright-mcp-server` when applicable?
    - Any remaining visual diff explicitly described?

13. Reuse manifest: reused components, new components, and non-reuse reasons clearly listed?

## Output Format (before code block)

BEFORE outputting any code, MUST print the following checklist:

```text
✅ Colors: simplified classes text-primary-6, bg-success-1 (no arbitrary values)
✅ Spacing: gap-* only (no margin)
✅ Radius: Button=6px, Card=8px
✅ Icons: all names match Figma data-name | all SVG files exist in public/icons/ | no hardcoded colors
✅ Components: reused [List components used]
✅ Typography: 14/22 body, 22/32 H5
✅ Dark mode: .dark compatible
✅ Annotations: data-component present
✅ Responsive: w-full, no 1440px
✅ shadcn: primitives from ui/
✅ Fidelity: typography/effects mapped | unmapped tokens listed when needed
✅ Visual validation: Figma screenshot checked | local screenshot checked | remaining diffs noted
✅ Reuse manifest: reused components | new components | reasons
```

Then print these sections in order:

1. `Reuse manifest`
1. `Token mapping summary`
1. `Unmapped tokens`
1. `Visual diff notes`

If ANY item fails, mark it ❌, fix it in code first, THEN output.
